quran[62]{c,v,t}:
  37,83,Dájúdájú (Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm wà nínú ìjọ (tí ó tẹ̀lé ìlànà) rẹ̀
  37,84,(Ẹ rántí) nígbà tí òun náà dojú kọ Olúwa rẹ̀ pẹ̀lú ọkàn mímọ́
  37,85,"(Rántí) nígbà tí ó sọ fún bàbá rẹ̀ àti àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀ pé: \"Kí ni ẹ̀ ń jọ́sìn fún"
  37,86,Ṣé ẹ̀ ń gbèrò láti sọ irọ́ di ọlọ́hun lẹ́yìn Allāhu
  37,87,Kí sì ni èrò ọkàn yín sí Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá?”
  37,88,Ó ṣíjú wo àwọn ìràwọ̀ gan-an
  37,89,"Ó sì sọ pé: \"Dájúdájú ó rẹ̀ mí"
  37,90,"Nítorí náà, wọ́n pa á tì, wọ́n sì lọ"
  37,91,"Nígbà náà, ó lọ sí ọ̀dọ̀ àwọn òrìṣà wọn. Ó sì sọ pé: \"Ṣé ẹ ò níí jẹun ni"
  37,92,Kí ni ó ṣe yín tí ẹ ò sọ̀rọ̀
  37,93,"Nígbà náà, ó dojú lílù kọ wọ́n pẹ̀lú ọwọ́ ọ̀tún (ó sì rún wọn wómúwómú)"
  37,94,(Àwọn abọ̀rìṣà) sáré wá dojú kọ ọ́
  37,95,"Ó sọ pé: \"Ṣé ẹ óò máa jọ́sìn fún n̄ǹkan tí ẹ gbẹ́ kalẹ̀ lére ni"
  37,96,Allāhu l’Ó sì dá ẹ̀yin àti n̄ǹkan tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́
  37,97,"Wọ́n wí pé: \"Ẹ mọ ilé kan fún un, kí ẹ sì jù ú sínú iná"
  37,98,Wọ́n gbèrò ète sí i. A sì sọ wọ́n di ẹni yẹpẹrẹ
  37,99,"Ó sọ pé: \"Dájúdájú mo máa lọ sí (ìlú tí) Olúwa mi (pa mí láṣẹ láti lọ). Ó sì máa tọ́ mi sọ́nà (láti dé ibẹ̀)"
  37,100,"Olúwa mi, ta mí lọ́rẹ ọmọ nínú àwọn ẹni rere"
  37,101,A sì fún un ní ìró ìdùnnú (nípa bíbí) ọmọkùnrin aláfaradà
  37,102,"Nígbà tí (ọmọ náà) dàgbà, tí ó tó bá (bàbá rẹ̀) ṣe iṣẹ́, (bàbá rẹ̀) sọ pé: \"Ọmọ mi, dájúdájú èmi lá àlá pé dájúdájú mò ń dúńbú rẹ. Nítorí náà, wòye sí i, kí ni o rí sí i.\" Ó sọ pé: \"Bàbá mi, ṣe ohun tí Wọ́n pa láṣẹ fún ọ. O máa bá mi nínú àwọn onísùúrù, tí Allāhu bá fẹ́"
  37,103,"Nígbà tí àwọn méjèèjì juwọ́ jusẹ̀ sílẹ̀, tí (Ànábì ’Ibrọ̄hīm) sì dojú (ọmọ) rẹ̀ bolẹ̀"
  37,104,"A pè é (báyìí) pé, ’Ibrọ̄hīm"
  37,105,o kúkú ti mú àlá náà ṣẹ. Dájúdájú báyẹn ni Àwa ṣe ń san àwọn olùṣe-rere ní ẹ̀san (rere)
  37,106,"Dájúdájú èyí, òhun ni àdánwò pọ́nńbélé"
  37,107,A sì fi àgbò ńlá ṣèràpadà rẹ̀
  37,108,A tún fún un ní orúkọ rere láààrin àwọn ẹni ìkẹ́yìn
  37,109,Àlàáfíà kí ó máa bá (Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm
  37,110,Báyẹn ni A ṣe ń san àwọn olùṣe-rere ní ẹ̀san (rere)
  37,111,"Dájúdájú ó wà nínú àwọn ẹrúsìn Wa, àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo"
  37,112,"A tún fún un ní ìró ìdùnnú (nípa bíbí) ’Ishāƙ, (ó máa jẹ́) Ànábì. (Ó sì máa wà) nínú àwọn ẹni rere"
  37,113,Àti pé A fún òun àti ’Ishāƙ ní ìbùkún. Ẹni rere àti alábòsí pọ́nńbélé (t’ó ń ṣàbòsí sí) ẹ̀mí ara rẹ̀ wà nínú àrọ́mọdọ́mọ àwọn méjèèjì
  37,114,Dájúdájú A ṣoore fún (Ànábì) Mūsā àti Hārūn
  37,115,A gba àwọn méjèèjì àti ìjọ àwọn méjèèjì là kúrò nínú ìbànújẹ́ ńlá
  37,116,A tún ṣàrànṣe fún wọn. Àwọn ni wọ́n jẹ́ olùborí (ọ̀tá wọn)
  37,117,A sì fún àwọn méjèèjì ní Tírà t’ó yanjú
  37,118,A tún fi àwọn méjèèjì mọ̀nà tààrà
  37,119,A fún àwọn méjèèjì ní orúkọ rere láààrin àwọn ẹni ìkẹ́yìn
  37,120,Àlàáfíà kí ó máa bá (Ànábì) Mūsā àti Hārūn
  37,121,Dájúdájú báyẹn ni Àwa ṣe ń san àwọn olùṣe-rere ní ẹ̀san (rere)
  37,122,"Dájúdájú àwọn méjèèjì wà nínú àwọn ẹrúsìn Wa, àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo"
  37,123,Dájúdájú (Ànábì) ’Ilyās wà nínú àwọn Òjíṣẹ́
  37,124,"(Ẹ rántí) nígbà tí ó sọ fún ìjọ rẹ̀ pé: \"Ṣé ẹ ò níí bẹ̀rù Allāhu ni"
  37,125,"Ṣé ẹ óò máa pe òrìṣà kan, ẹ sì máa fi Ẹni t’Ó dára jùlọ nínú àwọn ẹlẹ́dàá sílẹ̀, وَهُوَ خَيْرُ ٱلْحَٰكِمِينَ Òun l’Ó sì dára jùlọ nínú àwọn olùdájọ́. (sūrah al-’A‘rọ̄f 7:87) وَهُوَ أَسْرَعُ ٱلْحَٰسِبِينَ Òun sì yára jùlọ nínú àwọn oníṣirò. (sūrah al-’Ani‘ām 6:62) olùdájọ́ aláàánú ìbáà mọ bíi ọmọ iná igún àfi kí Allāhu jẹ́ Ẹlẹ́dàá rẹ̀. Kódà àdámọ́ owó àti okòwò tí wọ́n sọ di “ọrọ̀-Ajé. Àwọn t’ó ń bọ́ ẹlòmíìràn náà ń sọra wọn di olùpèsè. Yàtọ̀ sí pé Allāhu ti fi rinlẹ̀ pé Òun nìkan ni Olùpèsè fún gbogbo ẹ̀dá Rẹ̀. Tí èyí kò bá tí ì dá àwọn kan lójú bẹ́ẹ̀ tí wọ́n sì fẹ́ gbé gbogbo ìpèsè olúkùlùkù lórí ìwọ̀n nínú àánú tí Allāhu fi sí àwọn ẹ̀dá kan lọ́kàn ni wọ́n fi di aláàánú. Nítorí náà Allāhu ni Aláàánú jùlọ nínú àwọn aláàánú"
  37,126,"(ẹ̀ ń fi) Allāhu (sílẹ̀), Olúwa yín àti Olúwa àwọn bàbá yín, àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́"
  37,127,"Wọ́n sì pè é ní òpùrọ́. Nítorí náà, wọ́n máa mú wọn wá sínú Iná"
  37,128,"Àfi àwọn ẹrúsìn Allāhu, àwọn ẹni ẹ̀ṣà"
  37,129,A fún un ní orúkọ rere láààrin àwọn ẹni ìkẹ́yìn
  37,130,Àlàáfíà kí ó máa bá (Ànábì) ’Ilyās
  37,131,Dájúdájú báyẹn ni Àwa ṣe ń san àwọn olùṣe-rere ní ẹ̀san (rere)
  37,132,"Dájúdájú ó wà nínú àwọn ẹrúsìn Wa, àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo"
  37,133,Dájúdájú (Ànábì) Lūt wà nínú àwọn Òjíṣẹ́
  37,134,(Ẹ rántí) nígbà tí A gba òun àti gbogbo àwọn ará ilé rẹ̀ là
  37,135,Àyàfi arúgbóbìnrin kan tí ó wà nínú àwọn t’ó ṣẹ́ kù lẹ́yìn (láààrin àwọn tí A parẹ́)
  37,136,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A pa àwọn yòókù run"
  37,137,Dájúdájú ẹ̀yin náà kúkú ń gba ọ̀dọ̀ wọn kọjá láàárọ̀-láàárọ̀
  37,138,àti ní alaalẹ́. Ṣé ẹ ò níí ṣe làákàyè ni
  37,139,Dájúdájú (Ànábì) Yūnus kúkú wà nínú àwọn Òjíṣẹ́
  37,140,(Ẹ rántí) nígbà tí ó sá lọ sínú ọkọ̀ ojú-omi t’ó kún kẹ́kẹ́
  37,141,Ó sì bá wọn muje pọ̀. Ó sì wà nínú àwọn tí aje ṣí mọ́ lórí
  37,142,"Nítorí náà, ẹja gbé e mì; ó sì ń dá ara rẹ̀ lẹ́bi"
  37,143,"Nítorí náà, tí kò bá jẹ́ pé ó wà nínú àwọn olùṣàfọ̀mọ́ fún Allāhu"
  37,144,dájúdájú ìbá wà nínú ẹja títí di ọjọ́ tí wọn yóò gbé ẹ̀dá dìde